---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="MADECEM AI | Automatización Inteligente">
	
	<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 md:pt-48 md:pb-32 overflow-hidden">
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/grid.svg')] bg-center [mask-image:linear-gradient(180deg,white,rgba(255,255,255,0))]"></div>
		
		<div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
			<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 font-bold text-sm mb-8 animate-fade-in-up">
				<span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
				  <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-blue-400 opacity-75"></span>
				  <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-blue-500"></span>
				</span>
				Ingeniería de IA aplicada a Negocios Físicos
			</div>
			
			<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-8 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-white/60">
				Recupera tu tiempo.<br/>
				<span class="text-blue-500">Automatiza lo aburrido.</span>
			</h1>
			
			<p class="text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
				Creamos agentes de IA que atienden a tus clientes, gestionan citas y organizan pedidos mientras tú te dedicas a lo importante: tu oficio.
			</p>
			
			<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
				<a href="#contacto" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg transition-all hover:scale-105 shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/25">
					Auditoría Gratuita
				</a>
				<a href="#soluciones" class="text-slate-300 hover:text-white px-8 py-4 font-bold transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
					Ver Soluciones <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-24 bg-[#010413]">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-6">No es magia, es <span class="text-blue-500">Ingeniería</span></h2>
				<p class="text-slate-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
					Sustituimos tareas manuales repetitivas por sistemas autónomos robustos.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all group hover:-translate-y-1">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-blue-500/20 transition-colors">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Atención 24/7</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
						Agentes de voz y texto que responden dudas, dan precios y filtran clientes curiosos de los reales.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-all group hover:-translate-y-1">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-purple-500/20 transition-colors">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Agendamiento</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
						Tu calendario se llena solo. El sistema negocia huecos libres y confirma asistencia sin molestarte.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-all group hover:-translate-y-1">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-emerald-500/20 transition-colors">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-emerald-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Gestión de Pedidos</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
						Entrada de pedidos por WhatsApp transcritos automáticamente a tu ERP, Excel o TPV.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="soluciones" class="py-24 border-t border-white/5 scroll-mt-24">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-6">
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-4">Sectores 2026</h2>
					<p class="text-slate-400 text-lg max-w-xl">
						Soluciones verticalizadas listas para desplegar en 48 horas.
					</p>
				</div>
				<a href="/empresa" class="text-white font-bold hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
					Ver todos los sectores <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
				</a>
			</div>

			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
				
                <a href="/negocios/taller" class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:border-orange-500/50 transition-colors group relative overflow-hidden">
					<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
					<div class="relative z-10">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-orange-500">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z" />
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-orange-500 transition-colors">Talleres Mecánicos</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Gestión automática de citas, estado del vehículo y recambios.</p>
					</div>
				</a>

                <a href="/negocios/carniceria" class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:border-red-500/50 transition-colors group relative overflow-hidden">
					<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
					<div class="relative z-10">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-red-500">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 9V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2m2 4h10a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H9a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm7-5a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-red-500 transition-colors">Carnicerías</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Pedidos por WhatsApp directos a lista de corte y balanza.</p>
					</div>
				</a>

                <a href="/negocios/restaurante" class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-colors group relative overflow-hidden">
					<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-500/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
					<div class="relative z-10">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-yellow-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-yellow-500">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-yellow-500 transition-colors">Hostelería</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Reservas de mesa automáticas y gestión de carta digital.</p>
					</div>
				</a>

                <a href="/negocios/peluqueria" class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:border-pink-500/50 transition-colors group relative overflow-hidden">
					<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-500/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
					<div class="relative z-10">
						<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-pink-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-pink-500">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.121 14.121L19 19m-7-7l7-7m-7 7l-2.879 2.879M12 12L9.121 9.121m0 5.758a3 3 0 10-4.243 4.243 3 3 0 004.243-4.243zm0-5.758a3 3 0 10-4.243-4.243 3 3 0 004.243 4.243z" />
							</svg>
						</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-pink-500 transition-colors">Peluquerías</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Agenda inteligente, recordatorios de cita y cancelación automática.</p>
					</div>
				</a>

			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section id="contacto" class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#010413] to-blue-950/20">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-8">¿Listo para dejar de trabajar en tareas de robots?</h2>
			<p class="text-xl text-slate-400 mb-10">
				La primera consulta es gratuita. Analizamos tus procesos y te decimos cuánto dinero estás perdiendo en tareas manuales.
			</p>
			<form class="max-w-md mx-auto space-y-4">
				<input type="email" placeholder="tu@empresa.com" class="w-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-6 py-4 text-white placeholder-slate-500 focus:outline-none focus:border-blue-500 transition-colors" />
				<button type="submit" class="w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-xl transition-all hover:scale-[1.02] shadow-xl shadow-blue-600/20">
					Solicitar Auditoría
				</button>
				<p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-4">Sin compromiso. Respuesta en menos de 2 horas.</p>
			</form>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>